column5: Trying to figure out the name of a kids show I watched in the late 70's/early 80's, it had a lobster and hermit crab as characters I think, they were puppets and lived on a coral reef? Does anyone remember this show?
Were they like hand puppets?  There was a shark, dolphin and a seagull or something?
Who lives in a pineapple under the sea, SPONGEBOB SQUAREPANTS!!!!  I know that's not it, but I couldn't resist.
This link might help....  The Waterville Gang  If not then try this one...lists many children's shows for many decades  TV Shows  Bly
